original: Danielsson, Gustaf Kaleb, kyrkoherde, Tjugosjö, f. 4/8/02 i Bredsätra, Kalmar 1., av hemm:äg. August D. o. Mathilda Elofsson. G. 36 m. Agnes Rosberg. Barn: Eva f. 38, Lena 41, Ulla 42. — Stud:ex. i Kalmar 22, teol. fil. ex. i Lund 23, teol. kand., prakt, teol. prov samt prästv. f. Växjö stift 26. Tjg. s. v. pastor i S. Sandsjö, iVlmundsryd o. Ljuder, ständig adj. i Almundsryd, past:adj. i Bolstad samt stiftsadj., kyrkoh. i Ljuder sed. 36. Skr.: predikn. o. upps. i olika kyrkl. publ. samt i Smål:posten.
translated: Danielsson, Gustaf Kaleb, pastor, Tjugosjö, born August 4th, 1902 in Bredsätra, Kalmar 1., to home owners August D. and Mathilda Elofsson. Married for 36 years to Agnes Rosberg. Children: Eva born in 1938, Lena in 1941, Ulla in 1942. He graduated from Kalmar with his studentexamen in 1922, teol. fil. ex. from Lund in 1923, teol. kand., prakt, teol. prov and was ordained as a priest in the Växjö Diocese in 1926. He served as a pastor in S. Sandsjö,IVlmundsryd, and Ljuder, was a permanent assistant in Almundsryd, a pastoral assistant in Bolstad, and was ordained as kyrkoh. in Ljuder in 1936. He wrote sermons and essays for various church publications and in the Smålposten.
